<L>__{interior living room day}
<A>__{roy's place. roy enters from the bedroom, carrying a suitcase, which he drops on the sofa. he goes to one of the box framed clown pictures, takes it off the wall, puts it face down on the coffee table, removes two wing nuts holding the back, lifts off the back, and reveals stacks of money hidden inside. he takes two wads of money out, counting them, putting them on the coffee table, then fits the back in place, reattaches the wing nuts, and hangs the picture on the wall. stuffing the wads of money into the suitcase, he leaves.}
